                    "type": "linebreak",
                    "version": 1
                  },
                  {
                    "mode": "normal",
                    "text": "Born as Capture Classics, we started with period-perfect cars for screen, built on a racing background that taught us how to handle vehicles with care. As our clients and briefs expanded, so did we: modern hero cars, stunt builds, pro drivers, delivery, on-set support. Today, Spoke Hire connects bold ideas to the right vehicles—fast—for both productions and private moments.",
